/musr/command construct box           AlumPlate       60 90  5       G4_Al            0  0 -80   log_World           norot dead 265
/musr/command construct tubs          AlumPlateHole   0  25  5 0 360 G4_Galactic      0  0   0   log_AlumPlate       norot dead 267
